page_0: "They have not yet taken the castle. The Commander barricaded the doors at the central corridor. Now he and his surviving men are holed up behind there. Lady Vivianne was with them, thank heavens. I would not fancy her chances with all these leering thugs. If I ever get out of here, I will try to find my way through the sewer to reach them. I hope someone comes to rescue me soon. Before they threw me in here, I was wounded in the fighting. I seem to have lost quite a bit of blood. "
